1. prepare a USB Mac OS storage (HFS+)
2. restart your mac 
3. enter security mod (type cmd + r)
4. find termnimal and 
```cmd
csrutil disable  #close rootless
```
5. restart your mac
6. create a filed on your USB strage and name it "Backup"
```cmd
/Volumes/stragename/iphoe/Backup
```
7. open cmd and go to these table
```cmd
cd /Users/usrname/Library/Application Support/MobileSync
```
8. type 
```cmd
ln -s /Volumes/stragename/iphoe/Backup
```
9. you can back up your iphone now

10. restart your mac
11. enter security mod (type cmd + r)
12. find termnimal and 
```cmd
csrutil enable  #opne rootless
```
13. restart
